---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="SocialProof for Pilates Studios — Testimonials That Fill Your Classes | SocialProof"
  description="Collect and display authentic client testimonials for your pilates studio. Turn happy regulars into the social proof that books new members. Free to start."
>
  <main class="for-page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">For Pilates Studios</p>
        <h1>Your members get real results — let their words fill your classes</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Pilates delivers transformation: posture, core strength, pain relief. But new clients can't feel that until they try. SocialProof captures member results as testimonials that convert browsers into bookings.</p>
        <div class="cta-group">
          <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Start free — no credit card</a>
          <a href="/docs/quickstart" class="btn btn-secondary">See how it works</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pain">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Why pilates studio social proof falls flat</h2>
        <div class="pain-grid">
          <div class="pain-card">
            <h3>😤 Google reviews are hit or miss</h3>
            <p>Your best members never leave reviews. They love you, they refer friends, they just don't think to post on Google. Meanwhile one cranky drop-in from 2019 sits at the top.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-card">
            <h3>📸 Transformation stories live in your head</h3>
            <p>You know the member who came in with chronic back pain and now teaches reformer. That story is worth ten ads — but it's not on your website.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-card">
            <h3>🔗 New clients can't tell studios apart</h3>
            <p>Someone searching "pilates near me" sees five studios. Your site has no testimonials. Theirs has five. Who do you think they book with?</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="solution">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>SocialProof fixes this in 3 steps</h2>
        <ol class="steps">
          <li>
            <strong>Send a collect link</strong>
            <p>After class milestones — 10th class, 3-month anniversary, first reformer session — text or email your members a link. They share their experience in 60 seconds.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Approve with one click</strong>
            <p>Review submissions in your dashboard. Approve the ones you love. Keep the authentic, specific stories about back pain gone, posture transformed, core strength found.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Embed on your site</strong>
            <p>One script tag on your homepage or class schedule page. Looks beautiful on Squarespace, Wix, MindBody, or wherever you run your studio site.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Built for Pilates Studios</h2>
        <div class="feature-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>⭐ Star ratings + text</h3>
            <p>Collect written testimonials with optional star ratings. Show visitors exactly what to expect from your instructors and format.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>📷 Member photos</h3>
            <p>Let members add a photo. Real faces from real clients build the trust that studio renders and stock photos never can.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🎨 Matches your studio brand</h3>
            <p>Customize colors and layout so the widget looks native — minimal and clean, like your studio.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>📱 Mobile-first form</h3>
            <p>Members fill it on their phone right after class, when the endorphins are still flowing and they're most enthusiastic.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🔒 You own the data</h3>
            <p>Testimonials live in your SocialProof account. Not locked to Google, Yelp, or any third-party platform.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🆓 Free forever tier</h3>
            <p>1 active widget, unlimited collections. Free forever for 1 active widget. No credit card to start.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pricing-cta">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Start collecting testimonials today</h2>
        <p>Free forever for 1 active widget. Pro is $9/mo for unlimited everything.</p>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get started free</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
